ger condominium and a P3-million cash prize from Megaworld Corporation now awaits two-time Olympic gold medalist Carlos Yulo.\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 232, \"end\": 239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3269923166215198e-14, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megaworld_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Megaworld Corporation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megaworld_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megaworld_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company upgraded its reward to Yulo just hours after the gymnastreigned in the men's artistic gymnastics vault finalon Sunday, August 4, just a day after Yulo also finished first in themen's artistic gymnastics floor exercise finalon Saturday.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5707078694714474e-25, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since this is a very significant milestone in the history of Philippine sports to have two gold Olympic medals during our 100th year participation as a country in the Olympics, which also coincides with our company's 35th anniversary this year, we are boosting our reward for Carlos Yulo now totaling to P35-million,\\\" Megaworld President Lourdes Gutierrez-Alfonso said in a statement on Monday, August 5.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lourdes\", \"score\": 0.9599679672917829, \"rank\": 0.041701216293041715, \"text\": \"Lourdes\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lourdes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lourdes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He truly deserves this and we will always be proud of him for taking Filipino excellence to the next level.\\\"\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo will now get a three-bedroom condominium at McKinley Hill, instead of the previous two-bedroom unit the property company announced.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The condominium - which comes with two balconies, a separate maid's room, and a parking slot - will be turned over \\\"designed and fully furnished.\\\"\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is just one of the incentives Yulo will get upon his return to the motherland.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The government, other private companies, and some brands have already announced rewards for Filipino athletes returning with medals from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Under Republic Act 10699 or the National Athletes and Coaches Benefits and Incentives Act, Olympic gold medalists will be awarded P10 million.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"House Speaker Martin Romualdez on Monday said Yulo will also be getting at least P6 million from the lower chamber after securing the country two gold medals.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speaker_of_the_House_of_Representatives_of_the_Philippines\", \"score\": 0.7380175472585309, \"rank\": 0.3549811263159644, \"text\": \"House Speaker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speaker_of_the_House_of_Representatives_of_the_Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speaker_of_the_House_of_Representatives_of_the_Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9780166207012352, \"rank\": 0.022477510835982695, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5707078694714474e-25, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Philippine Olympic Committee will also award Yulo with a house and lot.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1992, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"te